title: representation
pid: 93bcccbc-6ba3-4e17-80fd-cd5846560de7
body: |2-
  Each is defined by a two-member relationship
    where the two members' types might differ.
    Even if untyped, left and right can still be referred to,
    if they need to be distinguished.
  For one kind of bidimensional collection node,
    everything in the left position is in the relationship
    with everything in the right.
  For the other, each left-right pair is listed explicitly.
